Package com.itkolleg.bookingsystem.domains

Class Timeslot

java.lang.Object
com.itkolleg.bookingsystem.domains.Timeslot
@Entity public class Timeslot extends Object
This class represents a time slot in the system. It provides different static time slot constants which represent typical booking time periods. timeslots objects are saved in the database.
